dct_title_s: Afbeeldinge van de Cabo St. Augustin
dct_description_sm: Bird's eye view of Cabo de Santo Agostinho.
Depicts the taking of the Portuguese settlement at Cape St. Augustin in Brazil by a Dutch fleet.
Shows buildings, fort, harbor, ships, figures, vegetation.
From Commelin's Histoire de la vie & actes memorrables de Frederic Henry Prince de Nassau Prince d'Orange, 1656.
